A simple action game written in Ruby/SDL.

!Screenshot

http:../softs/down.png

!Download

https://github.com/yhara/down/releases

!Requirements

See [[README|https://github.com/yhara/down]]

!How to play

!! Buttons

* ← : Move left
* → : Move right

!! Items

||!name||!effect ||
||Star || Invincible ||
||Parachute || Slow down ||
||Weight || Speed up||

!! Scores

+1 point for each step.

